# fetch-gitignore

A script to download .gitignore files from GitHub.

## Installation

```bash
pip install fetch-gitignore
```

## Usage
```bash
fetch-gitignore Python
```

This will download the Python .gitignore file and save it as .gitignore in the current directory.
